input_str: A friend that owns an exotics pet shop sent me this photo and video of a Panther Chameleon donated to him by an owner who claimed that "he was doing everything right" but the lizard was acting sick. After seeing the video and the severe distress that the cham was in, I told my friend that I would take it and try to nurse it as best as I could, but the prognosis was exceedingly grim from just the video evidence that I was presented with.
